name: Items Not Listed
query:
select distinct i.item_code as "Item:Link/Item:400",i.ebay_product_id,i.ebaytwo_product_id,i.amazon_product_id,sle.warehouse as "Warehouse::120" from `tabStock Ledger Entry` sle inner join `tabItem` i on i.item_code=sle.item_code 
where sle.warehouse in ('Ready To Ship - Uyn','Ready To Ship - FZI')
and (((i.ebay_product_id="" or i.ebay_product_id is null)  and (i.ebaytwo_product_id="" or i.ebaytwo_product_id is null)) or (i.amazon_product_id="" or i.amazon_product_id is null)) and (i.item_code not in (select distinct ii.item_code from tabItem i inner join tabItem ii on ii.variant_of=i.item_code and (((i.ebay_product_id!="" or i.ebay_product_id is not null)  and (i.ebaytwo_product_id!="" or i.ebaytwo_product_id is not null)) or (i.amazon_product_id!="" or i.amazon_product_id is not null) ))) group by i.item_code
